Task Manager Backend

A simple and scalable backend API for managing tasks, built with Node.js, Express, and Mysql.
Supports CRUD operations, environment-based configuration, and follows clean folder structure.
Features

RESTful API for task management
Auth apis
Create, Read, Update, Delete tasks
Environment variable support using dotenv
Clean project structure
Error handling & middleware support

PROJECT STRUCTURE
backend/
│── src/
│   ├── app.js
│   ├── server.js
│   ├── config/
│   │    └── db.js
│   ├── middleware/
│   │    └── auth.middleware.js
│   ├── services/
│   │    └── auth.service.js
│   │    └── task.service.js
│   ├── views/
│   │    └── task.routes.js
│   │    └── auth.routes.js
│   └── models/
│   │    └── task.model.js
│   │    └── auth.user.js
│── .env
│── package.json
│── README.md


Clone the repo
git clone <repo-url>
cd backend

INSTALLING PACKAGES
npm install

Environment Variables
PORT=
JWT_SECRET=
HOST=
USER=
PASSWORD=''
DB=


RUN COMMAND
npm start


